Vitech America receives $ 7 . 5 mln order . Vitech America Inc said Tuesday it has received additional product orders amounting to $ 7 . 5 million from a retail chain in Brazil . The new orders , which are to be shipped during the first half of 1997 , were made by Casas Bahia , a consumer electronics retail chain based in Sao Paulo . Vitech assembles and sells its own brand name of personal computers , business systems integration and network equipment . 
